data.system_settings: LG Tribute 5, Latest Android OS Version
data.actual_result: You get the "Your settings have not been saved" message even though it just autosaved.
data.expected_result: The menu closes normally without any warning message
data.short_description: Save Warning does not recognize channel category autosave
data.steps_to_repro: -  Have a channel and a category - Go into the channel settings - change the category - See the text box saying that channel settings have been saved - press the back button
